comments: Looney (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact initiated by Payton (NYK) during his driving shot attempt.
Randle (NYK) attempts to deflect the pass and marginal contact occurs to Green's (GSW) arm on the follow-through after releasing his pass.
Gibson (NYK) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt by jumping to his side where he makes incidental contact with his teammate Barrett (NYK).
During the rebound, Randle (NYK) cleanly taps the loose ball away from Looney (GSW).
Barrett (NYK) gathers and takes a legal two steps before going into his shooting motion.
Green (GSW) brings his arm down and is no longer vertical when he makes contact to Barrett's (NYK) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in Rose's (NYK) path and absorbs the marginal contact to his side.
Gibson (NYK) makes contact with Curry's (GSW) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Looney (GSW) places two hands on Gibson (NYK) and extends into him, affecting his FOM.

Replay review of the foul called on Barrett (NYK) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. During his contest, Barrett (NYK) turns his body and delivers hip to hip contact that affects Oubre Jr.'s (GSW) driving shot attempt.
Oubre Jr. (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position on Payton (NYK) and makes clean ball contact to temporarily dislodge the ball.
During the drive, Looney (GSW) moves laterally and makes leg to leg contact with Payton (NYK) and the contact affects his SQBR.

Bazemore (GSW) reaches in and makes contact with the ball and as he slides his hand off of the ball, marginal contact occurs with Randle's (NYK) arm when the ball is already becoming loose.  Oubre Jr. (GSW) then cleanly dislodges the ball from Randle.
Oubre Jr. (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Randle (NYK) and cleanly dislodges the ball.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Barrett (NYK) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Barrett (NYK) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Oubre Jr. (GSW) legally contests and cleanly blocks Rose's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
